  position,
  animation,
  shadow,
  backgroundColor,
  shadowColor,
  textColor,
  opacity,

  supersonic,
} = inputs;

  message,
  duration,
  position,
  animation,
  shadow,
  backgroundColor,
  shadowColor,
  textColor,
  opacity,
  hideOnPress,
});
